leted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 原谅dz的无知555", "timestamp": 1606979335, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652174, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 134812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: （你们应该学了基变换这种东西吧，就是$P^{-1}AP$这种，显然不改变特征多项式，而取$P=\\begin{bmatrix}\\vec{x} & \\vec{y}\\end{bmatrix}$的话，$P^{-1}AP=\\begin{bmatrix}\\kappa & b\\\\ 0 & a\\end{bmatrix}$没毛病，然后特征多项式还是$(\\lambda-\\kappa)^2$，所以一定有$a=\\kappa$，我觉得这个思路挺自然", "timestamp": 1606979502, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 呃呃，现在在路上，不能及时回复，不过谢谢Carol了！", "timestamp": 1606979851, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652208, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 134812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: （不会做的题建议发树洞分享一下，carol发现自己的线代快忘光了，试图复习（", "timestamp": 1606980031, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 601, "w": 1080}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 134812, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "555，求问万洞第二小问怎么做啊？突然就没了思路…", "timestamp": 1606975933, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1606980033, "url": "th/thhazm35njvotkpztaglirocxbxntw25.jpeg", "vote": {}}}